<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="a26Sep1933"><font color="red">26 September 1933</font> <i>NLHW</i> (from Harriet Weaver to Paul L&eacute;on): I have as far as possible put other things aside in order to do what I blame myself very much for not having made a greater effort to do years ago &mdash; that is, to steep myself in his <i>Work in Progress</i> and try my hardest to cope with its difficulties. </div>
